; Sword-Vow Ruins - Ronin intro arena.
; Stone fortress courtyard. Burned ramparts. A throne hall in the distance.
; Enforcer Kazat the Iron-Faced waits at the throne. Mob waves of Tashmu's
; Footmen + Archers between you and him.

